You don‚Äôt get to take unlimited big bets in a single lifetime. You get a small number of windows where risk tolerance, energy, capital, and conviction align.

But what‚Äôs often missed is that these opportunities are finite. You can‚Äôt swing endlessly. Most of life is spent accumulating the resources‚Äîknowledge, capital, relationships‚Äîthat make the next swing possible.
